## ‚úÖ 2. **CDK Snippet: Auto-Create SSM Automation Documents**

Add this to your `DevopsAgentStack` to **auto-deploy safe remediation runbooks**.

### üìÅ In `lib/devops-agent-stack.ts` (add inside constructor)

```ts
// SSM Automation Document: Restart EC2 Instance
new ssm.CfnDocument(this, 'RestartEC2InstanceDoc', {
  content: {
    schemaVersion: '0.3',
    description: 'Safely restart an EC2 instance',
    assumeRole: 'arn:aws:iam::YOUR_ACCOUNT:role/AutomationServiceRole', // create this role separately
    mainSteps: [
      {
        name: 'restartInstance',
        action: 'aws:runInstances',
        inputs: {
          InstanceIds: ['{{InstanceId}}'],
          MaxErrors: '0',
          TimeoutSeconds: '600'
        }
      }
    ],
    parameters: {
      InstanceId: {
        type: 'String',
        description: 'EC2 Instance ID to restart'
      }
    }
  },
  documentType: 'Automation',
  documentFormat: 'YAML'
});

// SSM Automation Document: Rollback CodeDeploy
new ssm.CfnDocument(this, 'RollbackCodeDeployDoc', {
  content: {
    schemaVersion: '0.3',
    description: 'Rollback to last successful deployment',
    assumeRole: 'arn:aws:iam::YOUR_ACCOUNT:role/AutomationServiceRole',
    mainSteps: [
      {
        name: 'rollback',
        action: 'aws:executeAwsApi',
        inputs: {
          Service: 'codedeploy',
          Api: 'CreateDeployment',
          applicationName: '{{ApplicationName}}',
          deploymentGroupName: '{{DeploymentGroupName}}',
          ignoreApplicationStopFailures: true,
          autoRollbackConfiguration: {
            enabled: true,
            events: ['DEPLOYMENT_FAILURE']
          }
        }
      }
    ],
    parameters: {
      ApplicationName: { type: 'String' },
      DeploymentGroupName: { type: 'String' }
    }
  },
  documentType: 'Automation',
  documentFormat: 'YAML'
});
```

> üí° **Note**: Replace `YOUR_ACCOUNT` with your AWS account ID.  
> Create an **IAM role `AutomationServiceRole`** with trust policy for `ssm.amazonaws.com` and permissions for EC2/CodeDeploy.

---

## üèÅ Final Notes for Hackathon Submission

- ‚úÖ **LLM**: Bedrock (Claude 3.5) ‚Üí meets requirement  
- ‚úÖ **AgentCore**: Tool schemas + `toolUse` parsing ‚Üí meets ‚Äú‚â•1 primitive‚Äù  
- ‚úÖ **Autonomous**: Lambda executes SSM/Lambda without human input  
- ‚úÖ **Human-in-the-loop**: `notify_human` via SNS  
- ‚úÖ **External tools**: CloudWatch Logs, SSM, Lambda, SNS  
- ‚úÖ **Deployable**: CDK + Lambda + public repo

